CASE WHEN COALESCE(SLA_TARGET_DATE,'') <> '' AND SLA_TARGET_DATE <> '20691231' 
THEN to_date(TRIM(SLA_TARGET_DATE), 'yyyy-MM-dd') 
WHEN SLA_TARGET_DATE = '20691231' THEN to_date('9999-12-31','yyyy-MM-dd') 
ELSE to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-dd') END
